{"tid":2102074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"設假想敵警示 防現反習勢力","createTime":"2020-07-10T08:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T08:14:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d4ef1fcdd8e186468f4d57f5647432e1294455","tid":2102074,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200710/TPK34KQST2NQNWZE7QH2XNQXHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200710%2FTPK34KQST2NQNWZE7QH2XNQXHQ%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=df82b321\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200710%2FTPK34KQST2NQNWZE7QH2XNQXHQ%2F&h=1c2d433f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200710/TPK34KQST2NQNWZE7QH2XNQXHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n設假想敵警示 防現反習勢力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7ln09_rfV8zaok3pYkc8WShShCo=/640x409/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZVZH62Q2CPRDUK5SYHHDYJ2SJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7ln09_rfV8zaok3pYkc8WShShCo%3D%2F640x409%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZVZH62Q2CPRDUK5SYHHDYJ2SJE.jpg&h=b969c82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周永康倒台多年，當局仍藉口要清洗「周餘毒」。<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】時事評論員劉銳紹對本報指，中共前政法王周永康倒台後，習近平已對公、檢、法及司法系統進行多輪「摻沙」式清洗，相信現政法系高層無人敢公開挑戰或質疑習，但不排除仍有人心有不服，或背後對習指指點點，尤其在政法系中下層「目無中央、自把自為、執法犯法」大有人在，社會怨聲載道；習通過「教育整頓」設置假想敵，一方面重整政法系，另方面警示黨內同儕，防出現反習勢力。<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹指，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n防止黨內出現反習勢力的「定海神針」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四項任務「拿人」為首<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「延安整風」奠定毛澤東絕對權威<br />\n<br />\n劉指現時距離2022年中共二十大還有兩年，習就開始對政法系動手，名義仍用「清除周餘黨」，此為中共歷朝掌權者慣用手法，即設置假想敵，保持政治張力，令黨內無法出現挑戰者。<br />\n<br />\n官方《北京青年報》昨刊文為今次政法系「教育整頓」解畫，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n你才會明白為何當局用『史詩』來比喻此波行動。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者"}]}